If you plan to run MPI programs on the EC2, it's easier to have StarCluster installed.
Some links:  
    - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vC3lJcPq1FY
    - http://star.mit.edu/cluster/

If you plan to test and debug MPI programs on your machine, OpenMPI is a great tool:
    - http://www.open-mpi.org/
